Package: spatialkit
Title: Spatial Tessellation, Modeling, and Cross-Validation Toolkit
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Author", "Name", email = "author@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A modular toolkit for spatial analysis workflows including CRS
    management, Voronoi/Delaunay/grid tessellation, feature-to-polygon
    assignment, geographically weighted regression (GWR via GWmodel),
    Bayesian spatial GP regression (via brms), spatial cross-validation
    with block/buffered strategies, and model comparison. Provides an S3
    class system (spatial_fit) with consistent predict/fitted/residuals
    methods across model backends.
